videos.description: DJ Johnson skies for the pass and scores as Kansas State goes up 50-47.
videos.headline: Johnson scores down low

videos.description: Tarik Phillips drains the corner 3 and ties the game at 50.
videos.headline: Phillip's 3-pointer ties the game

videos.description: Down one in the final seconds, Kamau Stokes settles for an off-balance 3-pointer and misses as Kansas State falls to West Virginia 51-50.
videos.headline: Kansas State can't convert on final possession
